1. *Očekivao* sam najbolje rezultate.(I was expecting the best results.)
2. On je *očekivao* da će dobiti nagradu.(He was expecting to get a prize.)
3. Oni su *očekivali* da će uspeti da postignu željeni cilj.(They were expecting to succeed in achieving the desired goal.)
4. Ona je *očekivala* da će biti uspešna u svom poslu.(She was expecting to be successful in her job.)
5. *Očekivao* sam da ću biti srećan.(I was expecting to be happy.)